<div class="title">Flaky Skin</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Adderall XR)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Jailbird&Exact=1">Jailbird</a></div>


